{"body": "I don't think we should add this. Using `slice` and `[]` should work fine:\r\n\r\n```ruby\r\nirb(main):002:0> {id: 7}.slice(:id, :other)\r\n=> {:id=>7}\r\nirb(main):005:0> {id: 7}[:other]\r\n=> nil\r\n```\r\n\r\nextracting stuff that wasn't there in the first place seems like a special case and I don't think it warrants a core extension.\r\n\r\n/cc @steveklabnik @carlosantoniodasilva ", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/19880345", "created_at": "2013-06-23T20:15:10Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/11064#issuecomment-19880345", "updated_at": "2013-06-23T20:15:10Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 11064, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/senny", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/3d698e2872c07061a455d9e250861235?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fd1359f9934ee5a75ed441ffce412a0a1.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny/received_events", "gravatar_id": "3d698e2872c07061a455d9e250861235", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "senny", "type": "User", "id": 5402, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237d912bd3543c15100855c"}, "id": 19880345, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/11064"}
